➜哥大的老师会不会欣赏胡适？——从胡适留学期间的文字发表情况看
https://untranslatable.home.blog/2019/09/19/%e5%93%a5%e5%a4%a7%e7%9a%84%e8%80%81%e5%b8%ab%e6%9c%83%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e6%ac%a3%e8%b3%9e%e8%83%a1%e9%81%a9%ef%bc%9f-%e5%be%9e%e8%83%a1%e9%81%a9%e7%95%99%e5%ad%b8%e6%9c%9f%e9%96%93/	12820
<p>（康奈尔大学校内刊物，绮色佳当地报刊，未发表的讲演稿，包括两篇关于卜朗吟的文章，为数不少，但因只有地方性影响力，不计。《中国留美学生月报》影响力和传播范围存疑，暂时也不计。另有为<em>The Philosophical Review</em>撰写的他人论著摘要五篇，似为系里布置的任务，因为此刊物是康大哲学系出版的哲学专业杂志，影响力待考，亦不计。）</p>
<p><strong>1914</strong>&nbsp; <em>The New Republic</em>（一次读者投书），<em>The Outlook</em>（一次投书，一次投稿被摘引），<em>Syracuse Post-Standard</em>（一次，转录胡适致《新共和》书内容）</p>
<p><strong>1915</strong>&nbsp; <em>The Outlook </em>（一篇短文，系该刊物约稿，题为“China and Democracy”，简评袁世凯复辟企图）</p>
<p>（这三种杂志均为全国发行的著名刊物）</p>
<p><strong>1915&nbsp; Notes on Dr. Lionel Giles Article on the Tun Huang Lu&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><em>Journal of Royal Asiatic Society</em>, 1915, PP. 35-39.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1916&nbsp; DOES MIGHT MAKE RIGHT? INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS AND ETHICS </strong>（这是一篇会议论文，会议主题是国际关系，会议地点在康乃尔大学，收在会议论文集里，与会者有名家Angell）</p>
<p><em>Proceedings of the Conference on international relations </em>: held at Cornell University, Ithaca, N. Y., June 15-30, 1915. 论文集由WORLD PEACE FOUNDATION出版于BOSTON 1916&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1916&nbsp; The Fetish of the Open Door&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>Release May 21 , 1916 ,<em> Federal Council ol the Christ in Anierica</em>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1916&nbsp; Is There a Substitute for Force in International Relations? </strong>（此文参加征文比赛得奖，奖金一百美金。出版地为纽约。）</p>
<p>Prize essay, International Polity Club Competition, awarded June 1916.<em> International Conciliation: Special Bulletin</em>, (New York: American Association for International Conciliation, 1916), 15 pages.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1916&nbsp; Analysis of the Monarchical Restoration in China </strong>（此文发表于哥大校内刊物）</p>
<p><em>Columbia Spectator</em>, January 14, 1916 7.&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1916 A Review of Benoy Kumar Sarkar</strong>’s <em>Chinese Religion Through Hindu Eyes : A Study in the Tendencies of Asiatic Mentality </em>（书评）</p>
<p><em>The Hindusthanee Student</em> (Nov. 1916), pp. 1-3.</p>
<p><strong>1917&nbsp; CLASSICAL CONFUCIANISM</strong>. （这是书评，评的是Miles Menander Dawson, <em>The Ethics of Confucius: The Sayings of the Master and his Disciples upon the Conduct of the &#8220;Superior Man</em>”)</p>
<p><em>The Monist</em>, Vol. 27, No. 1 (JANUARY, 1917), pp. 157-160.</p>
<p><strong>1917&nbsp; Manufacturing the Will of the People&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><em>The Journal of Race Development </em>7, no. 3 (1917): 319–328.&nbsp;</p>
<p>(此刊物实为《外交季刊》的前身。)<br></p>